eya_def_tools.data_models.calculation_model_specification.CalculationModelSpecification
Specification of a model used in an energy assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the model. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_yield_assessment.EnergyYieldAssessment
IEC 61400-15-2 EYA DEF energy yield assessment data model.
Attributes: json_uri (Optional[str]): Unique URI of the JSON document. Default is None. title (str): Title of the energy assessment report. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. project_name (str): Name of the project under assessment. document_id (Optional[str]): The ID of the report document; not including the version when 'document_version' is used. Default is None. document_version (Optional[str]): Version of the report document, also known as revision. Default is None. issue_date (date): Report issue date in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD. contributors (list[ReportContributor]): List of report contributors (e.g. author and verifier) issuing_organisations (list[Organisation]): The organisation(s) issuing the report (e.g. consultant). receiving_organisations (Optional[list[Organisation]]): The organisation(s) receiving the report (e.g. client), if relevant. Default is None. contract_reference (Optional[str]): Reference to contract between the issuing and receiving organisations that governs the energy yield assessment. Default is None. confidentiality_classification (Optional[str]): Confidentiality classification of the report. Default is None. coordinate_reference_system (CoordinateReferenceSystem): Coordinate reference system used for all location data. measurement_stations (list[MeasurementStationMetadata]): List of measurement station metadata JSON document(s) according to the IEA Task 43 WRA Data Model. Default is []. reference_wind_farms (Optional[list[ReferenceWindFarm]]): List of reference operational wind farms. Default is None. wind_resource_assessments (Optional[list[WindResourceAssessment]]): List of wind resource assessments, including results, at the measurement station locations. Default is None. turbine_models (Optional[list[TurbineModel]]): List of wind turbine model specifications. Default is None. scenarios (Optional[list[Scenario]]): List of energy yield assessment scenarios. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_yield_assessment.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: scenario_id (Optional[str]): Unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (ConstrainedFloatValue): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. wind_resource_assessment_basis (Optional[WindResourceAssessmentBasis]): Measurement wind resource assessment basis for the scenario. Default is None. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (Optional[TurbineWindResourceAssessment]): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. Default is None. gross_energy_assessment (GrossEnergyAssessment): Gross energy yield assessment. plant_performance_assessment (PlantPerformanceAssessment): Plant performance assessment including net energy results.

eya_def_tools.data_models.organisation.Organisation

Attributes: name (str): Entity name of the organisation. abbreviation (Optional[str]): Abbreviated name of the organisation. Default is None. address (Optional[str]): Address of the organisation. Default is None. contact_name (Optional[str]): Name(s) of contact person(s) in the organisation. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.report_metadata.ReportContributor

eya_def_tools.data_models.result.Result
Set of results for an element of an energy assessment.
Attributes: label (Optional[str]): Label of the results. description (Optional[str]): Description of the data object. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Comments on the data object. Default is None. assessment_period (AssessmentPeriod(StrEnum)): Period of or in time that has been assessed and for which the results are applicable. Default is 'lifetime'. dimensions (Optional[tuple[ResultsDimension(StrEnum), ...]]): Dimensions along which the results are binned (all result values in the same results object must have the same dimensions). Default is None. statistics (list[ResultStatistic]): List of result statistic objects that each include result values for a specific statistic type.
